Class QuizImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.rmi.server.RemoteObject
      • java.rmi.server.RemoteServer
        • java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
          • QuizImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote, Quiz

    public class QuizImpl
extends java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
implements Quiz, java.io.Serializable
    Quiz class that create a quiz object and is saved in the ServerManagerImpl class Each Quiz is made up of a number of Question objects This class holds the quiz ID, Number of questions for this quiz, and Top Score
    Author:
    mikieJ
